quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  16,90,"Zvirokwazvo, Allah vanokomekedza kuita zvakarurama nezvakanaka, uye nekubatsira hama dzepedyo, uye vanorambidza kuita mabasa akaipa nekusatenda uye neudzvanyiriri. Vanokurairai, zvimwe mungava munorangarira"
  16,91,"Uye zadzisai chibvumirano chaAllah kana maita chibvumirano ichocho, uye musava munoputsa mhiko mushure mekunge madzitora, uye zvirokwazvo mave munotora Allah semumiriri wenyu. Zvirokwazvo, Allah vanoziva zvamunoita"
  16,92,"Uye musava munoita semukadzi uyo anorudunura shinda yaanenge aruka mushure mekunge yasimba, nekutora mhiko senzira yekunyengedzana pakati penyu, zvimwe rimwe dzinza ringawande kupfuura rimwe dzinza. Zvirokwazvo, Allah vanokuedzai nazvo. Uye zvirokwazvo vachava pazuva rekumutswa vanokuburitsirai pachena izvo zvamaipesana (umwe achitenda muhumwechete hwaAllah uye umwe achiramba)"
  16,93,"Uye dai Allah vaida, vaikuitai dzinza rimwe chete (muve vechitendero chimwe chete), asi vanoita kuti wavanoda arasike, uye vanotungamira wavanoda. Uye zvirokwazvo muchava munobvunzwa pane izvo zvamaiita"
  16,94,"Uye musatore mhiko dzenyu senzira yekunyengedzana pakati penyu, zvimwe tsoka ingatsvedze mushure mekunge yasimbiswa, uye kuti muravire zvakaipa (murango pasi pano) nekudzivirira kwamakaita vanhu nzira yaAllah, uye muchawana murango mukuru wakaomarara (Gehena)"
  16,95,"Uye musava munotengesa chibvumirano chaAllah nemari shoma. Zvirokwazvo, zvina Allah zvakanakira imimi kana muchiziva"
  16,96,"Zvese zvamunazvo zvichapera, asi zvina Allah hazviperi. Uye avo vanotsungirira, zvirokwazvo, tichavapa muripo wavo weizvo zvakanaka zvavaiita"
  16,97,"Upi neupi anoita mabasa akanaka, angave murume kana mukadzi, ari mutendi wechokwadi, tinomupa hupenyu hwakanaka (pasi pano), uye zvirokwazvo tichavapa muripo wavo weizvo zvakanaka zvavaiita (Paradhiso)"
  16,98,"Naizvozvo kana uchiverenga Qur’aan, kumbira kudzivirirwa kuna Allah kubva kuna Satani, akashorwa"
  16,99,"Zvirokwazvo, haana simba pamusoro peavo vanotenda uye vanoisa ruvimbo rwavo muna Tenzi vavo"
  16,100,"Simba rake (Satani) riri pane avo vanomuteerera nekumutevera, uye neavo vanosanganisa Allah nezvimwe zvinhu"